{"id": "1368054697461813268", "channel_id": "1364252054817869937", "type": 19, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "🫡 🌹", "timestamp": "2025-05-03T02:40:57.102000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["655338276554801152"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1367563548812902471", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1364252054817869937", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」蟲族羊媽狂氣減費bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1368054319286583376", "channel_id": "1367469935894466621", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "親愛的海之心：\n\n問題已知悉，戈雅會整理給校工進行查驗，祝您週末愉快（90度鞠躬）（吻手💋 ）\n\n戈雅敬上🌹", "timestamp": "2025-05-03T02:39:26.938000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🌹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1367469935894466621", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」《無bug空間的逆襲 ～ 一度被稱為bug空間的我逆活一世，在維修公告拿出證明自己無bug的真本事 ～》", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1368136646150848512", "channel_id": "1368136646150848512", "type": 0, "author_id": "1039630326890250360", "author_name": "rei_the_witch", "author_bot": false, "content": "One of Lily's cards are broken, both on computer and mobile.\nWhen you go to use \"strike to protect\" it causes the card to freeze, but only that card, it will fix if you click it again. \nI don't know what causes this... \nSee video below, sorry for its poor quality and it's lag...", "timestamp": "2025-05-03T08:06:35.192000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-05-03T08:08:03.352000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "😲", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1368136646721278044", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20250503-085900_Morimens.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 5999447, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1368136646150848512/1368136646721278044/Screen_Recording_20250503-085900_Morimens.mp4?ex=69cc294b&is=69cad7cb&hm=63b2109431c5547db1297a8cc48ab04e491963661cdfe358c75e9e5ebb8bf4ce&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368136646150848512", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」 Strike to protect Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1368139622944604190", "channel_id": "1368136646150848512", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "<@&1166257943742787615>", "timestamp": "2025-05-03T08:18:24.915000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368136646150848512", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」 Strike to protect Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1368170487297085500", "channel_id": "1368136646150848512", "type": 19, "author_id": "364412673275723779", "author_name": "zier.0", "author_bot": false, "content": "I had the same issue with Wanda's 4 cost and 3 cost cards in the past, and i'll put my thoughts on this if it helps the devs debug the issue\n\nI think that's mostly due to how all the \"card\"s are in the game - when the text is too long, you can scroll through the text by clicking and dragging the text - for some reason this isn't maybe entirely disabled during combat, so it tries to make you \"scroll\" through the card instead of selecting it to be used\n\nLily's strike to protect is very wordy, and so are wanda's 4 cost and 3 cost cards\n\nAs a temporary solution I just try to select the very edges of the card since you're still somewhat selecting the card and not the text inside it\n\n--------\n\n这是借助深度求索（DeepSeek）完成的翻译\n\n过去我在使用旺达的4费和3费卡牌时也遇到过同样的问题，以下是我的分析思路，或许能帮助开发者调试：\n\n我认为这主要与游戏中所有\"卡牌\"的设定机制有关——当卡牌文本过长时，玩家可以通过点击拖动文本来滚动阅读。这个问题可能源于战斗状态下未能完全禁用该滚动功能，导致系统误将玩家的卡牌选择操作识别为试图滚动卡牌文本（而非使用卡牌）。\n\n莉莉的\"守护打击\"技能描述非常冗长，旺达的4费和3费卡牌同样存在文本过长的情况。\n\n目前我的临时解决方案是尽量点击卡牌最边缘区域，这样能确保选中的是卡牌本体而非内部文本区域。", "timestamp": "2025-05-03T10:21:03.550000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1039630326890250360"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🛐", "emoji_id": null, "count": 4}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368136646150848512", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368136646150848512", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」 Strike to protect Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
{"id": "1368171209530806382", "channel_id": "1368136646150848512", "type": 19, "author_id": "1039630326890250360", "author_name": "rei_the_witch", "author_bot": false, "content": "Oh that makes sense. I will try doing the same, thank you! <:happy:1356053849894420683>", "timestamp": "2025-05-03T10:23:55.744000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["364412673275723779"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1368170487297085500", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1368136646150848512", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Answered」 Strike to protect Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
